This is a Python interface to SSIP.

The full range of SSIP commands is implemented,  including callback handling.
See the section "Python API" in the OpenTTS documentation for more
information.

If you have any questions, suggestions, etc., feel free to contact us at the
mailing list <opentts-dev@lists.opentts.org>.

-- Tomas Cerha <cerha@freebsoft.org>
-- Amended by Chris Brannon for OpenTTS.
